When we changed format for the dates in the search requests we used the rewrite filter to change these.  We did the field part for dates but not the sort part.

E.g. the following will cause an *ACK*.
{noformat}
/sr/jira.issueviews:searchrequest-xml/temp/SearchRequest.xml?updated%3Aprevious=-1w&tempMax=15&reset=true&sorter/field=datecreated&sorter/order=DESC
{noformat}

It doesn't like {{datecreated}}.

